lead_paragraph: Sixth-seeded Venus Williams stayed on track for a possible semi-finals clash with sister Serena by sprinting past German Julia Goerges to reach the third round of the U.S. Open on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Venus Rises to Occasion With Straight Sets Win
